Class BooleanDoubleImmutablePair

java.lang.Object
it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.booleans.BooleanDoubleImmutablePair
All Implemented Interfaces:
BooleanDoublePair, Pair<Boolean,Double>, Serializable
public class BooleanDoubleImmutablePair extends Object implements BooleanDoublePair, Serializable
A type-specific immutable Pair; provides some additional methods that use polymorphism to avoid (un)boxing.
